{"tid":518523,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[教狗]雪橇應該點教？","createTime":"2018-01-03T12:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T10:05:27.000Z","uid":34983,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9062d26718018df5d66375da1f1db145ba3136","tid":518523,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"有隻16個月大嘅雪橇<br />\n喺屋企嘅時候可以好乖<br />\n出到街瘋狂扯繩 用choke chain都照扯<br />\n其實佢一扯我 我就會停低<br />\n<br />\n而且見到大狗又會嬲 wuwu聲咁叫 毛都會樹起哂<br />\n細狗就無問題 可能由細到大都有隻貴婦陪佢<br />\n但亦都係咁 貴婦教壞哂佢<br />\n例如見到生寶人會wuwu聲咁叫<br />\n但佢唔係唔開心 唔係嬲<br />\n只係用錯聲<br />\n但就係咁令其他人覺得好得人驚<br />\n雖然佢從來唔會咬人<br />\n<br />\n真係覺得佢行為有問題<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5fdb924b06b4dd7daa0b8707ee8caaf0050c16","tid":518523,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d4a9161f73ec5ce30930073b4beca10a9fcfce9","tid":518523,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcad7a23578b8ebf8fc354730e312d0240948046","tid":518523,"uid":15406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"留名睇比人屌用choke chain"},{"pid":"f52a947902e397e208fdf4b725689e6e89393381","tid":518523,"uid":34983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50d6289a449bfbfd35a19b24e082ffcbad60f3e9","tid":518523,"uid":34983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bcad7a23578b8ebf8fc354730e312d0240948046","tid":518523,"uid":15406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"留名睇比人屌用choke chain"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"唔用choke chain我都比佢扯走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffcaacb4127a5292c59928dea215abf7aea06e0","tid":518523,"uid":59278,"like":1,"disli